briefdescription.para: Short term memory for component settings. Resets on loading of project or compiling.

memberdef.name: passthruLabel
memberdef.initializer: = new GUIContent( "Sync Pass Thru Methods", "'this.SetTrigger()', 'this.Play()', 'this.CrossFadeInFixedTime()', etc methods are provided by this class, and will pass through the same named commands to the Animator. " + "When enabled, these methods will be sent and triggered over the network. Disabling this allows these methods to act as if they were called directly on the Animator without any networking, which is convenient for testing.")

memberdef.name: statesLabel
memberdef.initializer: = new GUIContent( "Sync States", "When enabled, changes in the animator current state are transmitted.")

memberdef.name: layerWeightsLabel
memberdef.initializer: = new GUIContent( "Sync Layer Weights", "When enabled, changes to all layer weights will be synced.")

memberdef.name: paramsLabel
memberdef.initializer: = new GUIContent( "Sync Parameters", "When enabled, animator parameters will be networked and synced.")

memberdef.name: label_syncLayers
memberdef.initializer: = new GUIContent( "Sync Layers", "State syncs for all layers, rather than just the root layer.")

memberdef.name: label_Interp
memberdef.initializer: = new GUIContent( "Interp", "Interpolation enables lerping(tweening) of values on clients between network updates.")

memberdef.name: label_Extrap
memberdef.initializer: = new GUIContent( "Extrap", "Extrapolation replicates previous values if new values from the network fail to arrive in time. When disabled, values default to default value for that parameter as defined in the Animator")

memberdef.name: label_Default
memberdef.initializer: = new GUIContent( "Defs", "Default value used for initial values and extrapolation.")

memberdef.name: index_Default
memberdef.initializer: = new GUIContent( "Index Animator Names", "Polls Animator Controller for all State, Trigger and Transition hashes. Indexed values require a tiny fraction of bandwidth to send compared to raw 32 hashes. This happens often automatically, but it never hurts to press this button after making changes to your Animator Controller.")

memberdef.name: triggerLabel
memberdef.initializer: = new GUIContent("Triggers", "WARNING: Triggers tend to fire and clear instantly, resulting in a failure to sync. Use the this.Trigger() pass through call instead.")

memberdef.name: intGC
memberdef.initializer: = new GUIContent("", "How interpolaton is handed for this parameter. Interpolation occurs in Update() between application of net updates.")

memberdef.name: extGC
memberdef.initializer: = new GUIContent("", "How extrapolation is handed for this parameter. Extrapolation occurs when an update fails to arrive and a guess needs to be made for this value.")

memberdef.name: defGC
memberdef.initializer: = new GUIContent("", "The default value for this parameter when extropation occurs.")
